---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Home" bodyClass="home">
  <div class="home-layout">
    <aside class="home-sidebar">
      <img
        src="/images/profile.jpg"
        alt="Filippo Carmenati"
        class="profile-image"
        width="200"
        height="200"
      />
      <div class="social-buttons-container">
        <a
          class="social-button"
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/filippo-carmenati-5215ba1b4/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >LinkedIn</a>
        <a
          class="social-button"
          href="mailto:filippo.carmenati@gmail.com"
        >Email</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="home-content">
      <p class="hello"><strong>Hi there, were you looking for me?</strong></p>

      <p>
        I am a recent Dr. Sc. ETH Zurich in Agricultural Science graduated with a
        thesis titled:
        <a
          href="https://www.research-collection.ethz.ch/entities/publication/dd909597-43d4-42df-827f-3807a08f9964"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >“Agricultural diversification through the use of underutilized crops”</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Despite my scientific background and this rather “grand-sounding”
        title, I feel I have only scratched the surface of many things. My
        interests are quite interdisciplinary and driven by genuine curiosity.
        I could group them all under the broad and fascinating umbrella of
        interactions.
      </p>

      <p>
        The simple aim of this site is to try to bring what I write and think
        in my diaries into a space that is more accessible to everyone.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you’d like a slightly longer description of who I am, you can find
        it <a href="/about-me">here</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="home-section-heading">Academic interests</h2>
      <ul class="home-list">
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HEjD1-D2KLE"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Plant phenomics</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dCs2r4kpHKQ&t=33s"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Plant–plant interactions</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bVcLekZ_L90"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Plant phenotypic plasticity</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mOssYTimQwM&t=420s"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Gamification</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gCh89_4Jzo&t=131s"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Cereal–legume mixed cropping</a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="home-section-heading">Currently looking</h2>
      <ul class="home-list">
        <li>Postdoc positions</li>
        <li>
          Developing and testing a card game to teach crop-diversification
          effects
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
